9","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560273018","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545824653,"updated_time":1545824653,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":57,"content":"\u003cp\u003e在这个问题下为题主祝贺叫好的诸位忘了凡伟了吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/59471035/answer/165656590\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1825018d44043bb90a9f094b49317a79_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"2270\" data-image-height=\"1016\" class=\"internal\"\u003e如何评价凡伟提出的电荷不存在理论？\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e立个flag，这题主要是能证明哥猜，我哈士奇的哈字换个部首。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559785440,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"29448cc28212a543bea56b9492f82e25","url_token":"morgancheng","name":"程墨Morgan","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/04d3c071d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/04d3c071d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/29448cc28212a543bea56b9492f82e25","user_type":"people","headline":"互联网研发老兵，微信公众号morgansays，《深入浅出React和Redux》作者","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559785440","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545779269,"updated_time":1545779269,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":492,"content":"\u003cp\u003e肯定不会，如果高中生就证明了哥德巴赫猜想，那还清什么华什么北什么大？全世界任何一所大学你随便挑。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然而，醒醒，不要幻想着高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在中科院的附近，有段时间（也许现在还有）总能看到一些人在路边闲逛，眼神呆滞，看到有人路过，就递上去一个小条，上面三言两语几个公式“证明”了哥德巴赫猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这些人，就是被“证明哥德巴赫猜想就可以直接进高等学府”这种想法耽误的人。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561746835,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"e0ce809ba0adc98e09e7cd55dcdf9901","url_token":"lian-ke-30","name":"假语","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7f20c63f898cb67cf0620d862011fc7f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7f20c63f898cb67cf0620d862011fc7f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/e0ce809ba0adc98e09e7cd55dcdf9901","user_type":"people","headline":"十分冷淡存知己，一曲微茫度此生。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561746835","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545995761,"updated_time":1546003532,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":193,"content":"\u003cp\u003e一个人群嘲失败了，是哗众取宠的小丑。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个人群嘲成功了，那就是睥睨四顾的成功人士了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你看，刚刚骂人家骂得正爽，觉得这种脑子的人这辈子都不能成功，可是一转眼，他现在就已经从一个民科升华成了一个移动的流量大v了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e虽然他现在看起来还是个民科也或者高一新生。但是你看看别人关注数量，很多人拿赞同数量举例。其实他们根本不明白赞同和关注的区别\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d25c224c83666220bfb82aca032c6b88_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='1480'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d25c224c83666220bfb82aca032c6b88_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e再看看别人的回答流量，虽然不知道他本意是否是炒作。但是这19k的关注。和浑身上下自带的流量，加上知乎这个平台对于高关注用户的偏爱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而且，19k的关注远远不是终点，现在热度还没有停止呢，并且知乎也在为了热度恶意的引导着流量\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e很多人不相信我，那我便举几个例子。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-873718197d230676a4bd114a04b858ef_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-189dfb2f18f13a950983e375a04f6735_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-873718197d230676a4bd114a04b858ef_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='1480'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-189dfb2f18f13a950983e375a04f6735_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-873718197d230676a4bd114a04b858ef_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-873718197d230676a4bd114a04b858ef_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e比如这位叶青大v，他积攒了几年的粉丝为18k。用了几年的时间，而最开始他还仅仅只是一个不知名用户的时候，就依靠阅读流量获得了极多邀请合作，以及在答案里面植入广告的邀请。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而我们的高中生，证明大v。却坐拥19k的活跃用户关注，其中还包括不少大v。也就是他最少也足以在短期内达到叶青大v层次的水平，一些说只值几百块钱的朋友，我只能说你对于流量变现太没有概念了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4a105753bf6a5a3a0b6357c059e54ca5_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-332a112e8701690a2baa07e90efa66ea_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4a105753bf6a5a3a0b6357c059e54ca5_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='1480'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-332a112e8701690a2baa07e90efa66ea_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4a105753bf6a5a3a0b6357c059e54ca5_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4a105753bf6a5a3a0b6357c059e54ca5_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b681d3de365f887656932acf0ebb33d7_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-55ac1a6ce35f310e36bb2b29f0b34ce0_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b681d3de365f887656932acf0ebb33d7_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='1480'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-55ac1a6ce35f310e36bb2b29f0b34ce0_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b681d3de365f887656932acf0ebb33d7_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b681d3de365f887656932acf0ebb33d7_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e而这个问题的流量更是可怕至极，如图所示。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e目前来说他的帐号价值已经上了六位数以上了。这是什么意思。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也就是人家选择最愚蠢的变现方式，把这个账号卖了。也足以变现数十万了，至于其他的各种变现方式，最简单就是成为一个大v开一个公众号。流量变现。足以让他在高中就月入五位数，如果经营得好。足以让自己年收入比得上一个小资家庭的年收入了，高考加分也无非请人代笔发表一篇简简单单的论文再背上一背。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e现在这个帐号那怕是拿来给我这种不怎么熟悉知乎各种潜规则的人来运用，也足以达成月入过万这种小目标，而给某些人能够产生的流量更是难以直接计算。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e想想人家高一就能赚数十万，想出如此的完美炒作方式。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那怕是哗众取宠。人家也已经成功了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个案例足以位列知乎最近三年成功的钓鱼案例。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们对于钓鱼者的冷嘲热讽也无非是在赠送流量，为他的变现添砖加瓦。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也不知道是有预谋的炒作还是天意如此。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我只知道，他确实成功了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个成功者，还是值得我献上一点敬意的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那怕，靠的只是运气\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560667253,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"242dd9f71ffc0da37adb60670312514f","url_token":"dong-tian-wen-35-51","name":"董天文","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-0d06eac6c33af85b5cc1848d76cfd6cf_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-0d06eac6c33af85b5cc1848d76cfd6cf_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/242dd9f71ffc0da37adb60670312514f","user_type":"people","headline":"数学建模多次最高奖得主/吹水指导","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560667253","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545878061,"updated_time":1545878061,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":84,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不玩知乎的我也来吃瓜了...\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560461710,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560461710","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-1e0cdf5e487ef87fdcb501e3dbfc89c9_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545839596,"updated_time":1546068718,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":141,"content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e12.29更新：\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e偶然在网上发现了科学出版社2011年出版的《哥德巴赫猜想》（第二版，潘承洞、潘承彪著\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e）的试读章节链接。感兴趣的可以点击\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.ecsponline.com/yz/B64EDB42D69214CEEB63DA63C7A996100000.pdf\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e这个链接\u003c/a\u003e下载。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e虽然只有引言，但恕我直言，贵乎上能完全读懂引言的人可能不超过【数据删除】个。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有志于研究哥猜者可以去某宝或某东购买全书，并不算太贵。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e况且，再次恕我直言，\u003cb\u003e真正\u003c/b\u003e有能力研究哥猜的人应该都能够接触到图书馆。至少我查了敝校的图书馆，还是有几本的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a31240b415dd25db97fc13c124076529_b.jpg\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1748\" data-rawheight=\"745\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a31240b415dd25db97fc13c124076529_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1748\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a31240b415dd25db97fc13c124076529_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1748'%20height='745'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1748\" data-rawheight=\"745\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a31240b415dd25db97fc13c124076529_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1748\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a31240b415dd25db97fc13c124076529_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a31240b415dd25db97fc13c124076529_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e就是这本书\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e千万要注意\u003c/b\u003e不要买到徐迟所著的那个同名报（ji）告（tang）文学。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e今天哥猜能成为民科聚集地，不可谓没有上面那本报告文学的“功劳”呢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e------------------12.29分割线------------------\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在知乎上发表……您会吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f956d2cf9e33c9ae796fcc80cade6ee9_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"924\" data-rawheight=\"716\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f956d2cf9e33c9ae796fcc80cade6ee9_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"924\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f956d2cf9e33c9ae796fcc80cade6ee9_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='924'%20height='716'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"924\" data-rawheight=\"716\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f956d2cf9e33c9ae796fcc80cade6ee9_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"924\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f956d2cf9e33c9ae796fcc80cade6ee9_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f956d2cf9e33c9ae796fcc80cade6ee9_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果不会的话，还有4天，学会Latex公式语法足够了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e学会Latex语法之后，在数学方面的顶级期刊发文章也是没问题的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果您说您的证明“根本用不到这些需要用公式编辑器才能打出来的玩意”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对不起\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e慢走不送\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e-----------12.27更新分割线-----------\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这位仁兄似乎开了个叫“数学”的专栏……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e估计证明方法就会发在里面吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e居然有些期待呢（x\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（1）如果半年后他真的能进入大学学习数学，这个专栏可能会成为一个能够交流数学（*真正的数学）的地方。如果真的有那一天，希望大家都忘记他当年年轻气盛时曾经声称证明了哥猜吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e （2）如果不然，那里想必要变成民科理论聚集地了。真是可怕。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e衷心希望最后结果（1）成立。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如下为陈景润论文里的一个公式。我当然完全看不懂\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e但我至少没有声称自己证明了哥猜\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cnotag%5Csum_%7BD%3Cq%5Cleqslant+Q%7D%5E%7B%7D%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B%5Cvarphi+%28q%29%7D%7B%5C+%7D+%7B%5Csum_%7B%7B%5Cchi%7D_q%7D%5E%7B%7D%7D%5E%7B%5Cast+%7D%7B%5Cleft+%7C+%5Csum_%7Bn%3DM%2B1%7D%5E%7BM%2BN%7D+a_n+%7B%5Cchi%7D_%7Bq%7D%28n%29%5Cright+%7C%7D%5E%7B2%7D%5Cleqslant+%5Csum_%7Bi%3D0%7D%5E%7Bh%7D%5Cleft+%28%5Csum_%7B2%5EiD%3Cq%5Cleqslant+2%5E%7Bi%2B1%7DD%7D%5E%7B%7D%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B%5Cvarphi+%28q%29%7D%7B%5Csum_%7B%7B%5Cchi%7D_q%7D%5E%7B%7D%7D%5E%7B%5Cast+%7D%7B%5Cleft+%7C+%5Csum_%7Bn%3DM%2B1%7D%5E%7BM%2BN%7D+a_n+%7B%5Cchi%7D_%7Bq%7D%28n%29%5Cright+%7C%7D%5E%7B2%7D%5Cright+%29%5C%5C+%5Cnotag%5Cleqslant+%7B%7D+%5Csum_%7Bi%3D0%7D%5E%7Bh%7D%5Cleft+%28%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B2%5EiD%7D%5Cright+%29%5Cleft+%28%5Csum_%7B2%5EiD%3Cq%5Cleqslant+2%5E%7Bi%2B1%7DD%7D%5E%7B%7D%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B%5Cvarphi+%28q%29%7D%7B%5Csum_%7B%7B%5Cchi%7D_q%7D%5E%7B%7D%7D%5E%7B%5Cast+%7D%7B%5Cleft+%7C+%5Csum_%7Bn%3DM%2B1%7D%5E%7BM%2BN%7D+a_n+%7B%5Cchi%7D_%7Bq%7D%28n%29%5Cright+%7C%7D%5E%7B2%7D%5Cright+%29+%5C%5C%5Cnotag%5Cleqslant+%7B%7D+%5Csum_%7Bi%3D0%7D%5E%7Bh%7D%5Cleft+%282%5E%7Bi%2B2%7DD%2B%5Cfrac%7B%5Cpi+N%7D%7B2%5EiD%7D%5Cright+%29%5Csum_%7Bn%3DM%2B1%7D%5E%7BM%2BN%7D%5Cleft+%7Ca_n%5Cright+%7C%5E2%5Cll%5Cleft+%28Q%2B%5Cfrac%7BN%7D%7BD%7D%5Cright+%29%5Csum_%7Bn%3DM%2B1%7D%5E%7BM%2BN%7D%5Cleft+%7Ca_n%5Cright+%7C%5E%7B2%7D%5C%21\" alt=\"\\notag\\sum_{D\u0026lt;q\\leqslant Q}^{}\\frac{1}{\\varphi (q)}{\\ } {\\sum_{{\\chi}_q}^{}}^{\\ast }{\\left | \\sum_{n=M+1}^{M+N} a_n {\\chi}_{q}(n)\\right |}^{2}\\leqslant \\sum_{i=0}^{h}\\left (\\sum_{2^iD\u0026lt;q\\leqslant 2^{i+1}D}^{}\\frac{1}{\\varphi (q)}{\\sum_{{\\chi}_q}^{}}^{\\ast }{\\left | \\sum_{n=M+1}^{M+N} a_n {\\chi}_{q}(n)\\right |}^{2}\\right )\\\\ \\notag\\leqslant {} \\sum_{i=0}^{h}\\left (\\frac{1}{2^iD}\\right )\\left (\\sum_{2^iD\u0026lt;q\\leqslant 2^{i+1}D}^{}\\frac{1}{\\varphi (q)}{\\sum_{{\\chi}_q}^{}}^{\\ast }{\\left | \\sum_{n=M+1}^{M+N} a_n {\\chi}_{q}(n)\\right |}^{2}\\right ) \\\\\\notag\\leqslant {} \\sum_{i=0}^{h}\\left (2^{i+2}D+\\frac{\\pi N}{2^iD}\\right )\\sum_{n=M+1}^{M+N}\\left |a_n\\right |^2\\ll\\left (Q+\\frac{N}{D}\\right )\\sum_{n=M+1}^{M+N}\\left |a_n\\right |^{2}\\!\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=40\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=0\u0026sort_by=default","totals":2142}}
